songs.title: Baby Blue Eyes
songs.album: A Collection of Rare and Unreleased Recordings
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Every head is turned
Eyes opened wide
Look what just walked in tonight
What I left behing
What I never intended to find
Is hunting me, killing me
Can't get you out of my mind

[Chorus]
Baby Blue Eyes, the way that you walk in the room
I could leave off your smile
All this time your stealing me, breathless like he used to
Baby Blue Eyes, I can not
I can not get enough of you
Does it matter, how long it's been
In the end I still leave you

[Verse 2]
A reason of you brings me to my knees
I can't escape what I need
I'm fully aware he looks but don't touch
But honey you're teeling me, hanging it
Braving your love

[Chorus]
Baby Blue Eyes, the way that you walk in the room
I could leave off your smile
All this time your stealing me, breathless like he used to
Baby Blue Eyes, I can not
I can not get enough of you
Does it matter, how long it's been?
In the end I still need you

[Outro]
No, no, no, no, no
Baby blue eyes
I love you
Baby blue eyes, baby blue eyes
I still need you, no, no
Why, why, why, why?
Why do i constantly think of you in my head?
Why are you always near me in my bed?
Baby Blue Eyes
Baby Blue Eyes
Baby Blue Eyes
